reference "prop: Reduced Form Log Patents"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, so all buyers are symmetric, and we additionally assume that on average
 generic and specialized R&D productivity is the same.
 Now, we examine how patents differ across counties.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

