\begin_inset Formula $\zeta_{f,c}$
\end_inset

 for some 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 and low 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\zeta}_{f,j}/\bar{\zeta}_{f}$
\end_inset

.
