 Citations measure the direction of specialized model R&D:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{Citations_{f,j}}{\sum_{j}Citations_{f,j}}=\frac{I_{f,j}^{\varrho\gamma}}{\sum_{j}I_{f,j}^{\varrho\gamma}}\text{ and }\frac{Citations_{f,j,c}}{\sum_{j,c}Citations_{f,j,c}}=\frac{I_{f,j}^{\varrho\gamma}}{\sum_{j}I_{f,j}^{\varrho\gamma}}\frac{I_{f,j,c}\zeta_{f,j,c'}}{\sum_{c'}I_{f,j,c}\zeta_{f,j,c'}}
\]

\end_inset


