 R&D choices (see Proposition 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "prop: Supplier R&D Level and Prices"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

).
 
\begin_inset Note Note
status collapsed

