\begin_inset Formula $\nu$
\end_inset

.
 The terms 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{j,A}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{j,p}$
\end_inset

 represent R&D in assembly and parts, while 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{j,A,k}$
