\end_inset

, along with unobserved residual productivity components 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{j,A,c}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{j,p,c}$
\end_inset

.
 The elasticities 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau_{j}$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $,\tau_{jf}$
\end_inset

 govern how R&D productivity responds to local conditions.
 
