status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
where 
\begin_inset Formula $d_{j,A,c}$
\end_inset

 is the distance of an OEM to its assembly plants and 
\begin_inset Formula $d_{j,p,c}$
\end_inset

 is the distance to suppliers of part 
