\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 (see Appendix for caluclation) and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{1}\left\{ \text{Multinational R\&D}\right\} $
\end_inset

 is an indicator for the multinational R&D scenario.
